# AI-Powered Helmet Violation Detection System

## Features

- Custom YOLOv8 Helmet Detection Model
- OpenCV Video Processing
- Violation Detection Engine
- Analytics Engine
- Evidence Snapshot Generation
- FastAPI Backend (In Progress)
- PostgreSQL Integration (In Progress)
- Docker Deployment (Planned)

## Tech Stack

- Python
- YOLOv8
- OpenCV
- FastAPI
- PostgreSQL
- SQLAlchemy
- Docker
- Bootstrap
- Jinja2

